        <abstract> 
<p>Sends <hi rend="italic">Nepenthes laevis</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Wallace for the Royal Medal is a good thought.</p>
            <p>W. H. Harvey is at Kew and JDH has asked him about desert climbers.</p>
